  "texts": [
    "Conversation patterns revolve around the interaction between machines and humans through various forms of conversation and communication such as voice, text, illustrations, and images.",
    "This pattern involves two-way interaction, where both machines communicate with humans and vice versa.",
    "The overall goal of Conversation Patterns is to bridge the gap between humans and machines in terms of communication.",
    "This fosters more natural and effective information exchange, supports applications such as automated chatbots, content generation, and language translation, and improves human-machine interaction.",
    "(Walch, 2019)."
